<h1 >麦子</h1>
<h2>（农业作物）</h2>
<a href="javascript:;" class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" href="javascript:;" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=14670" target="_blank" class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" nslog-type="90000102"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num"></span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">麦子，单子叶植物，<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A6%BE%E6%9C%AC%E7%A7%91/2458872" data-lemmaid="2458872">禾本科</a>。一年生或二年生草本植物。茎秆中空，有节。叶长披针形。穗状花序称“麦穗”，小穗两侧扁平，有芒或无芒。<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A2%96%E6%9E%9C/4856035" data-lemmaid="4856035">颖果</a>即麦粒。按播种期分<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%86%AC%E5%B0%8F%E9%BA%A6">冬小麦</a>和<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%98%A5%E5%B0%8F%E9%BA%A6/508357" data-lemmaid="508357">春小麦</a>。</div><div class="para" label-module="para">麦子，世界各地都有<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%A0%BD%E5%9F%B9/12003577" data-lemmaid="12003577">栽培</a>。子粒主要制<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%9D%A2%E7%B2%89/1215215" data-lemmaid="1215215">面粉</a>，皮可作<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A5%B2%E6%96%99/2438924" data-lemmaid="2438924">饲料</a>，麦秆可用于编织等。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
